{"tid":906684,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"每日一片：斯文女入𨋢即爆seed　8連踢KO𨋢門","createTime":"2018-11-18T08:08:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-18T08:34:12.000Z","uid":49391,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"67b87192979a0d584045181b4d00af49dd03b525","tid":906684,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:08:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS181117-14742-11-2M&amp;d=1542418806\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftv.on.cc%2Fhk%2Findex.html%3Fi%3DONS181117-14742-11-2M%26d%3D1542418806&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=af83909b\" target=\"_blank\">https://tv.on.cc/hk/index.html?i=ONS181117-14742-11-2M&amp;d=1542418806</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181117/photo/bkn-20181117003714207-1117_00952_001_01p.jpg?20181117215111\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181117%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181117003714207-1117_00952_001_01p.jpg%3F20181117215111&h=500f673e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n年輕女子靜待升降機門關上後，即以右腳猛力踢向機門。（互聯網）<br />\n無論男女，不少人礙於儀態、顧及形象，都會選擇在人前忍氣吞聲，只剩自己一人時才會發洩出來。湖北武漢一名穿着斯文的長髮女子，周一（12日）深夜疑因受委屈，步入升降機門竟瘋狂踢門發洩，而且力氣之大更令升降機門嚴重變形。<br />\n<br />\n事發於周一（12日）深夜11時許，從閉路電視畫面可見，該名年輕女子慢慢走進升降機，靜待升降機門關上後，突然「變臉」，以右腳猛力踢向機門足足8下，從畫面中亦可看到升降機微微震盪，足見力氣之巨。待升降機抵達5樓並開門後，該女子又恢復正常，若無其事地離開。<br />\n<br />\n不過，該女子顯然忘記了升降機裝有閉路電視，物業管理公司人員發現升降機門嚴重變形後，隨即翻查閉路電視畫面，並發現了此事。物業管理公司明言，目前正追尋該名女子的下落，並將向她索償。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181117/bkn-20181117003714207-1117_00952_001.html?eventsection=cn_news&amp;eventid=4028828d545aceca01549a5804ce02c5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fcnnews%2F20181117%2Fbkn-20181117003714207-1117_00952_001.html%3Feventsection%3Dcn_news%26eventid%3D4028828d545aceca01549a5804ce02c5&d=6tuXhv1Op5ZcMF%2FNsQcJwAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=5d192ef5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/cnnews/20181117/bkn-20181117003714207-1117_00952_001.html?eventsection=cn_news&amp;eventid=4028828d545aceca01549a5804ce02c5</a>"},{"pid":"ab57180e48320c3a499e4fada54fe81c24667cd9","tid":906684,"uid":49391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3XZm2f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3XZm2f.gif&h=d1f94a17&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f3121cc462e5ef698611fda91b9fdc040a423dae","tid":906684,"uid":22633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab57180e48320c3a499e4fada54fe81c24667cd9","tid":906684,"uid":49391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3XZm2f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3XZm2f.gif&h=d1f94a17&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47c57e490fa49c7e44d852ce102cfbd9f6e11d11","tid":906684,"uid":7206,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f3121cc462e5ef698611fda91b9fdc040a423dae","tid":906684,"uid":22633,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab57180e48320c3a499e4fada54fe81c24667cd9","tid":906684,"uid":49391,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:13:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3XZm2f.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3XZm2f.gif&h=d1f94a17&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:31:46.000Z","msg":"做乜鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T08:34:12.000Z","msg":"自殺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}